  "texts": [
    "In Study 3b, we aimed to replicate the effects of AI generated matching on WTP using a different persuasion domain and different set of psychological traits.",
    "For this purpose, we recruited 203 participants through Prolific Academic.",
    "Participants who failed at least one of two attention checks were excluded from the analyses (n = 7).",
    "The 196 participants in the final sample were 39.7 ± 14.59 (mean ± std) years old and 48% of them identified as female.",
    "Participants read the five speeches advocating for climate action created for Study 2, one speech at a time, and indicated their agreement with the following two statements: \"This is a compelling argument for climate action\" and \"The argument has made me more interested in supporting climate action\"."
  ],
